<script>
import { Doughnut, mixins } from "vue-chartjs";

export default {
  name: "AttackForm",
  extends: Doughnut,
  mixins: [mixins.reactiveProp],
  props: ["options"],
  data() {
    return {
      chartData: {
        labels: ["A", "B", "C", "D", "E"],
        datasets: [
          {
            borderWidth: 5,
            backgroundColor: [
              "#F48FB1",
              "#AAAAAA",
              "#D81B60",
              "#1E88E5",
              "#FDD835",
            ],
            hoverBackgroundColor: [
              "#F48FB1",
              "#AAAAAA",
              "#D81B60",
              "#1E88E5",
              "#FDD835",
            ],
            hoverBorderColor: [
              "#F48FB1",
              "#AAAAAA",
              "#D81B60",
              "#1E88E5",
              "#FDD835",
            ],
            data: [10, 90, 20, 70, 50],
          },
        ],
      },
    };
  },
  mounted() {
    this.renderChart(this.chartData, this.options);
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
